 ago with her husband and children then aged six and eight since then the family has embraced the british way of life  even giving the most recent addition to the family a seven month old daughter the very english name of emma  and gasperment feels fully settled in london i dont plan to move on she says in her spare time she enjoys taking the family to concerts and music festivals music in london is so much more accessible than in paris she says its more relaxed and is of a fantastic quality here you go to a concert because you like music and you are passionate about it it is not highbrow like it is in france or some sort of social display gasperment also enjoys picking up english colloquialisms and has a small book in which she notes any she finds particularly amusing  favourite entries include a bird in the hand is worth two in the bush and not counting your chickens before they are hatched she cites her balance of work and family life as one of her biggest achievements i have been able to thrive professionally and have my family and enjoy seeing them develop she says her secret may be her insistence that whatever the day has in store she sits down for a very early breakfast with her children her favourite part of her job is teambuilding … subscribe today subscribe to questia and enjoy full access to this article and over  million more from academic journals magazines and newspapers over  books access to powerful writing and research tools article details publication marketing publication date june   subjects gasperment sophiemanagement loreal uk ltdofficials and employees cosmetics industryofficials and employees subscribe today subscribe to questia and enjoy full access to this article and over  million more from academic journals magazines and newspapers over  books access to powerful writing and research tools article details publication marketing publication date june   subjects gasperment sophiemanagement loreal uk ltdofficials and employees cosmetics indust